<i>The sun's in my heart
and I'm ready for love.</i>

1085
01:40:45,744 --> 01:40:48,044
<i>Let the stormy clouds chase...</i>

1086
01:40:50,620 --> 01:40:51,960
Arrêtez-la !

1087
01:40:54,130 --> 01:40:57,090
C'est la voix de cette jeune fille
qui vous a enchantés.

1088
01:40:57,250 --> 01:41:01,300
C'est elle, la vedette de notre film !
Kathy Selden !

1089
01:41:08,844 --> 01:41:12,444
<i>You are.</i>

1090
01:41:12,544 --> 01:41:16,344
<i>My lucky star.</i>

1091
01:41:17,644 --> 01:41:21,244
<i>I saw you.</i>

1092
01:41:21,344 --> 01:41:24,144
<i>From afar.</i>

1093
01:41:26,244 --> 01:41:28,344
<i>Two lovely eyes.</i>

1094
01:41:28,444 --> 01:41:33,820
<i>At me they were gleaming.</i>

1095
01:41:33,844 --> 01:41:37,920
<i>Beaming</i>

1096
01:41:37,944 --> 01:41:43,820
<i>I was starstruck.</i>

1097
01:41:43,844 --> 01:41:47,544
<i>You're all.</i>

1098
01:41:47,644 --> 01:41:52,444
<i>My lucky charms</i>

1099
01:41:52,544 --> 01:41:56,644
<i>I'm lucky.</i>

1100
01:41:56,744 --> 01:42:01,444
<i>In your arms.</i>

1101
01:42:01,544 --> 01:42:05,744
<i>You've opened heaven's portal.</i>

1102
01:42:05,844 --> 01:42:11,644
<i>Here on Earth
for this poor mortal.</i>

1103
